                <title>House Districts of Indiana Current</title>
                <geoform>vector digital data</geoform>
            </citeinfo>
        </citation>
        <descript>
            <abstract>House boundaries for the state of Indiana, passed in October of 2021.</abstract>
            <purpose>This dataset contains polygon features representing the boundaries of the current 123rd Indiana General Assembly House districts. These districts were redrawn after the 2020 decennial census redistricting process and were adopted by the Indiana General Assembly in October of 2021. This data was obtained from the State of Indiana's Legislative Services Agency in August 2022 and IGIO staff added attributes for each representative's name, party affiliation, and website on 10/17/2023.</purpose>
        </descript>
